{"tid":2151039,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外媒接公司電話︰勿得罪警方","createTime":"2020-08-11T07:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T08:57:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6bfbb483abb512c36215abf185d98aea98b7912b","tid":2151039,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/445UCYWUM7TOQPACEMLPC2SLUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F445UCYWUM7TOQPACEMLPC2SLUQ%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=6df4cbd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2F445UCYWUM7TOQPACEMLPC2SLUQ%2F&h=a2ff6bff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/445UCYWUM7TOQPACEMLPC2SLUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n外媒接公司電話︰勿得罪警方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y6hBz65eNa0yr9aXl-K2BXstLeM=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M7XI6V7KEDAISMCDAXS5SCPCL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy6hBz65eNa0yr9aXl-K2BXstLeM%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM7XI6V7KEDAISMCDAXS5SCPCL4.jpg&h=0f44ff58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方在昨日的行動中出動流動指揮車。<br />\n<br />\n【本報識】警方昨大舉搜查壹傳媒大樓，直接衝擊新聞自由，而在大樓外，針對傳媒採訪的安排同樣視新聞自由如無物，先在壹傳媒大樓外劃出範圍極大的封鎖線，拒讓傳媒接近大閘作採訪，之後更對現場傳媒作審查，只揀選部份進入封鎖線內採訪。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：堅守崗位，撐到底！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n封鎖大樓外整條街<br />\n<br />\n有被篩走的記者即場據理力爭，「問佢（警察）有咩準則先可以入去，唔答，問入去幾耐，都唔答，問會唔會換人，一樣唔答。」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n就昨日的採訪情況可見，雖然警方搜查只涉及壹傳媒大樓，但卻把大樓閘外。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當負責帶隊搜查壹傳媒大樓的國安處高級警司李桂華昨於大樓向記者交代案件。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n海外傳媒也不准接近大樓，據悉有外媒記者不久後接獲公司來電，「叮囑」不要得罪警方，隨後有外媒陸續撤離現場。"},{"pid":"ab1ee68a5e1a31f3ad834037182312889c92c33e","tid":2151039,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd905b93f6f96a767798d99125eb14d98d285a0e","tid":2151039,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131f36b96f279f965f1d907e732cfd13ef91cbdb","tid":2151039,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"不如自己做埋採訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac633b4ad168bf309f538c96829c119b2bd185d5","tid":2151039,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"Pussy <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58cd72f6e0ce380be35bc835baae9f0e0b04501","tid":2151039,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:42:43.000Z","msg":"勿得罪社會寄生蟲"},{"pid":"4270c21ec3c6a87db9a682305028e14d645b4ec8","tid":2151039,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab11d165ce69489a86c5896ea4035b26ecb9475","tid":2151039,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"外媒係咪怕香港office比警察搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2787c1ffe5c7454bb2d404b6f4495a4d21d6450","tid":2151039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"叫勿得罪狗隻個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal